title: Ep.15: Jake Paul, Urban Meyer, Lions Beat Arizona, NFL Playoff Picture, Steelers Chances, and More.
description: Jake Paul has been impressive albeit against much smaller guys that aren't boxers. Its about time he chooses the right fight. Urban Meyer gets his long overdue firing. Can he go back to becoming an NCAA powerhouse? This is Green Bays Super Bowl to lose as they are undoubtedly atop the NFL. Tune in for more!
dc:creator: Griffin Proctor & Joe Jokonya
